## License Structure

This repository contains only framework documentation and the pre-paper.
No source code is hosted here — code lives in the layer-specific sub-repos
(L2, L3, L4), each with their own license.

| Scope | Files | License |
| ----- | ----- | ------- |
| Research & Documentation | `README.md`, `CAL_PrePaper_v1.3.md`, `docs/`, all `.md` files | CC BY-NC 4.0 |

