## Intellectual Property Notice

The **Cognitive Abstraction Layers (CAL)** architecture, the **Semantic
Information Density (SID)** metric, and all associated theoretical
constructs were conceived and formalized by Juan Pablo Chancay.

This repository serves as a timestamped public record of the original
contribution, establishing intellectual priority prior to formal academic
publication.

- Pre-paper first published: May 2026 — DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.20430343
- Repository: <https://github.com/jpcpol/Cognitive-Abstraction-Layer-CAL>

